b'Super Mario World: Mario to Yoshi no B: b'Super Mario World: Mario to Yoshi no Bouken Land is an interactive anime video based on the game Super Mario World. It is designed for use with Bandai\'s Terebikko system, which utilizes a telephone-shaped microphone to "interact" with the video. It asks the viewer multiple choice questions, such as what will hatch from Yoshi\'s egg.\n\n(Source: Mario Wiki) '
